createProjectImpact(string,string,string.details: SECURITY: Called ONLY by WorkApprovalResolver after full validation of work approval **Security Model:** - ONLY callable by WorkApprovalResolver (trusted contract) - Resolver verifies user identity BEFORE calling this function - Two-layer security: 1) Resolver validates operator status, 2) This checks caller is trusted - Operators CANNOT call this directly - prevents bypassing approval flow

createProjectMilestone(string,string,str.details: SECURITY: Called ONLY by AssessmentResolver after full validation **Security Model:** - ONLY callable by AssessmentResolver (trusted contract) - Resolver verifies user identity BEFORE calling this function - Two-layer security: 1) Resolver validates operator status, 2) This checks caller is trusted - Operators CANNOT call this directly - prevents bypassing assessment flowThird parameter (milestoneMeta) is intentionally unused - kept for API compatibility with AssessmentResolver

proxiableUUID().details: Implementation of the ERC1822 {proxiableUUID} function. This returns the storage slot used by the implementation. It is used to validate the implementation's compatibility when performing an upgrade. IMPORTANT: A proxy pointing at a proxiable contract should not be considered proxiable itself, because this risks bricking a proxy that upgrades to it, by delegating to itself until out of gas.
